KPC Android App released.
Download the app: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=org.hackesta.kpcexplorer

Features:
All photos are fetched from @kashphotoclub 's Facebook Group

Multiple Sections:
All Photos:
View photos without any filter or sorting

Categories:
View photos by choosing a category (Landscapes, Street Photography, etc)

Favorites:
View photos which ahve been favorited by you

Offline Mode
You can use the app offline as well. The app stores the recent photos viewed by you, so incase you don't have an internet connection, you can still view previously viewed photos

Favorites
You can favorite any photo and view them in a separate section

Share the photo
You can share the viewed photo with people, and can also give credit to the photographer & KPC

Download the photo
You can download a high quality version of any photo

Multiple Qualities
You can set the quality you want to use while browsing in the app settings, and also choose the resolution of the photo you are downloading.

Visit Project Page: http://hackesta.org/projects/kpc/

Announcing the release of KPC Android App v0.4.0 - Beta

Changelog:
[Add] Can post Text only posts
[Add] Can choose quality to use while browsing and downloading
[Add] Can browse in a single column view
[Fix] Unknown character bug in displaying/posting EXIF
[Fix] App returns to Main Screen after starting upload
[Change] App name changed from KPCExplorer to KPC

Future plans

Add upload progress (waiting for bug fix from Facebook)
Add watermark feature while posting new photo
